description.en:
GHPU–Global Hash Power Union/The Global Computing Alliance Foundation, launched by Bitcoin enthusiasts and miners worldwide, was established in September 2018. The industries involved by the members of the Foundation include mining machine research and development, mining field construction, mining machine investment, mining pond construction, digital encrypted wallet and other computing industry chains.

GHP Token Bitcoin anchoring is supported by global mine owners and miner investors.

GHPU will build an efficient and economic Bitcoin mining ecosystem, bringing sustained and stable returns to the Global Computing Alliance Foundation and investors.
